name: Pretty Little Fears
description:
The artwork story :
I'm loving your light,
vulnerable Letting your guard down is honorable
Specially when the past ain't been that friendly to you,
but there's magic in that You the flower that I gotta protect
And keep alive in the wintertime, hey, don't you die yet
You been way more than a friend of mine, we more like fam.
